Module Robotinterface

Package robotinterface.passives

Provides general access to robot passive elements, such as linear passive or axis-rotation passive. The can be uses as a type of servo to, e.g. measure a distance.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AxisRotationPassive
    An interface of a passive element that supports rotation over a single axis.
    FullRotationPassive
    An interface of a passive element that supports full rotation.
    LinearPassive
    An interface of a passive element that may have any length.
    Passive
    Upper interface to all passive elements.
